{"tid":800771,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"點解遊戲業中好似淨係得電競同pubg出名?","createTime":"2018-08-31T06:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T14:48:58.000Z","uid":80323,"like":2,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d19275392c6132b9b0354feeeea2a3ec8d263959","tid":800771,"uid":80323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:41:41.000Z","msg":"近年外國同香港hit電競，開始出名到連社會大眾、唔打機既人都識，今年財政預算案仲撥款1億發展電競。<br />\n<br />\n但係遊戲業唔止得電競，EA, Activision, ubsioft, Take-Two, Cd projekt red呢D發行商做到上埋市，微軟,Sony呢兩大公司自已亦都有出家用機，有遊戲業務，但係普羅大眾又唔知。VR亦都唔知有幾多人知道係因為遊戲而出現。仲有display card，無遊戲業既話3D加速卡,GPU, Nvidia同ATI都唔會出現。<br />\n<br />\n唔係覺得電競同lol唔好(pubg呢隻就緊係垃圾)，始終多左人認識同接受打機唔係壞事，但係遊戲業既其他部份，好似高技術遊戲同game engine，普羅大眾唔知就真係覺得好可惜。"},{"pid":"6d6fe250d27dc0ec18b0713beceacb8051e3c687","tid":800771,"uid":5793,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"啲廢老會同你講萬般皆下品 惟有讀書高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"448690842439ad65929d13270ab1771cb4f2367e","tid":800771,"uid":1085,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:21:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2070e2bb8d1dcc0c575e62c9e31e69634465d56","tid":800771,"uid":59742,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:22:39.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ee7b7369a1ea8616beba4e24bff749a80b0de1","tid":800771,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"之前買大要但玩唔夠兩個鐘refund"},{"pid":"5fc2e4339e965aa7d13cb9ff15bc35b22ece4b67","tid":800771,"uid":2471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T07:24:31.000Z","msg":"Dota2"},{"pid":"3693b536dbbb0a92f4c36f70b15a711331308a43","tid":800771,"uid":442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T09:42:37.000Z","msg":"香港gamedesign 大斷層<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asset